                  <summary>Psalter, ዳዊት፡, commissioned by Ḫaylä Śǝllase; One Miracle of the Virgin Mary, ተአምረ፡ ማርያም፡</summary>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="3v" facs="005"/><locus from="170r" to="171r" facs="174"/><title type="complete" ref="LIT2384Taamme"/></msItem>
